---
permalink: "/ragas/"
layout: base.njk
title: "Ragas"
description: "Notes on ragas — thaat, time of day, aroha-avaroha, and mood."
canonical: "/ragas/"
section: "ragas"
---
<div class="hero">
  <p class="eyebrow">The framework</p>
  <h1>Ragas</h1>
  <p class="lede">Each raga keeps its own hour and its own mood. Short notes on the ones I keep returning to.</p>
</div>

<div class="ornament">{{ ragas.length }} ragas</div>

<nav class="listing">
  {% for r in ragas %}
    <a class="entry" href="/ragas/{{ r.slug }}/">
      <span class="e-title">{{ r.name }}</span>
      <span class="e-poet">{{ r.samay }}</span>
      <span class="e-raga">{{ r.thaat }}</span>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</nav>
